Ok! 😁 this was my Mom’s #apron before she passed. I never told her, and in return she never knew. There’s always so much we wish we would have told the dead but never do. It’s a repeat cycle. Last week I had the opportunity to tour the new @biowarebase studio in EPCOR tower in our downtown. Many of you already know I’m a gamer and BioWare is my favourite gaming studio.

They have created my favourite games of all time including the @masseffect series. It’s wonderful to see them coming into our downtown as many people working for BioWare wanted to be downtown instead of their previous location.

Congratulations to on your new studio and I can’t wait to play your next creation!

caption.text:

Except one sloop. He was completely new and had already been sunk once. He got an alliance. Lol Stay frosty, pirates. 🤙🏴‍☠️🍍

Some more @playoverwatch plays with Symmetra with some beats I made in the back. Some of them fit the gameplay, some not really but I wanted to use em. 
With the update of role queue that doesn't allow swapping between roles, I'm probably not putting any more damage characters videos because I don't want to wait 8 minutes for a game to start (that's why I ditched League of Legends) which is good because this is one of the few good DPS characters I'm decent at anyways lol.
In any case, I have 4 beats between these snippets so I hope yall dig some of them. 
Feedback always appreciated.
